Provenance note:

The rows in this source are a project-owned fragment weight cap list written
directly by Chiaki.C to suppress non-lexical segmentation shards. Candidate
fragments were cross-checked offline against the Ministry of Education
Revised Mandarin Chinese Dictionary (CC BY-ND 3.0 TW) as a reference only;
that dictionary's text is not redistributed in this repository, and this
notice does not alter its license.
